snippet.title: Rise of Humanity - Steam Game Festival Teaser
snippet.description:
Hope you had a chance to play the Rise of Humanity alpha demo for free during the Steam Game festival (16-22 June 2020). 

Wishlist now! https://store.steampowered.com/app/1048530/Rise_of_Humanity/ and check out our registration page for alpha testing: https://riseofhumanitygame.com/alpha-beta-sign-up/
